data.description: Spacious updated home with lower level on a gentle 0.37 acre lot in the highly desirable Fountain Trace neighborhood of Hendersonville.  MULTIPLE LIVING OPTIONS with 3 BRs, 2 baths, ON MAIN LEVEL along with living, dining, fireplace and kitchen. Finished lower level en suite with additional living area and its own entrance is perfect as an in-law suite with minor modifications.  New roof (2023), new LVP flooring in primary suite (2023), new heat pump (dual for lower level), new kitchen with new granite countertops, cabinets, sink, faucet, paint and lighting (2021). All newer appliances convey including refrigerator, range, and microwave, washer/dryer and dishwasher.   This is a gem of a find in a coveted established neighborhood at a great price!  Fully fenced private backyard on .37 acres has space for outdoor living AND room to play.  Priced below appraised value. Assumable VA loan. Also listed 4045559.
